e%20materials%20and%20products%20you%20choose%20should%20correlate%20with%20the%20price%20point%20of%20your%20home%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20put%20a%20Frigidaire%20in%20a%20million-dollar%20property%2C%20that%20may%20not%20sit%20well%20with%20people.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20put%20a%20Viking%20stove%20in%20a%20lower%20price-point%20property%2C%20that's%20overkill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20customized%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBe%20careful%20with%20anything%20that%20is%20super%20custom%20to%20you%2C%20your%20taste%2C%20or%20your%20lifestyle%2C%20like%20a%20really%20unique%20wallpaper%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bull.%20%26quot%3BGo%20for%20it%20if%20you're%20OK%20knowing%20that%20it%20may%20not%20help%20your%20bottom%20line.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20pause%20and%20ask%20yourself%2C%20'If%20I%20do%20this%20upgrade%2C%20am%20I%20going%20to%20get%20enough%20value%20and%20enjoyment%20out%20of%20it%3F'%20Because%20you%20might%20not%20see%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20when%20you%20go%20to%20sell.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22744eca5c-acb1-4417-bf74-63b9ec0c495e%5C%22%3EFocus%20on%20the%20kitchen%20and%20bathrooms%20%E2%80%94%20and%20don't%20overthink%20the%20landscaping%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20set%20a%20budget%20for%20your%20renovation%2C%20prioritize%20the%20kitchen%20and%20bathrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKitchens%2C%20primarily%2C%20and%20baths%20sell%20houses.%20That's%20where%20you're%20generally%20going%20to%20get%20the%20most%20ROI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bull%2C%20adding%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20massive%20budget%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%20%26quot%3BYou%20might%20not%20have%20%2430%2C000%20to%20redo%20your%20whole%20kitchen%2C%20but%20maybe%20you%20have%20%2410%2C000%2C%20and%20you%20can%20reglaze%20your%20kitchen%20cabinets%20so%20that%20they're%20white%20or%20add%20some%20molding%20to%20them%20or%20put%20on%20new%20knobs%2C%20all%20of%20which%20will%20add%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElkins-Hutten%20agrees%20that%20you%20should%20spend%20time%20and%20money%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20sure%20the%20kitchen%20is%20organized%20for%20flow%20and%20for%20storage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20you%20have%20to%20rip%20out%20walls%20and%20stuff%20like%20that%2C%20but%20making%20sure%20you%20have%20nice%2C%20clean%20countertops%20and%20nice%2C%20shaker%20cabinets%20%E2%80%94%20something%20very%20simple%2C%20light%20colors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wouldn't%20spend%20a%20big%20portion%20of%20her%20budget%20on%20the%20landscaping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20never%20over-landscape%20a%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elkins-Hutten.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20what%20you%20think%20is%20beautiful%20for%20landscaping%2C%20I%20guarantee%20the%20next%20person%20is%20going%20to%20rip%20out%20and%20do%20something%20else%2C%20so%20just%20make%20it%20clean%3A%20clean%20lines%2C%20clean%20garden%2C%20clean%20paint%20on%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22859de8d4-8452-492e-b752-7724a8daeb99%5C%22%3ENew%20paint%20can%20go%20a%20long%20way%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bull%2C%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20the%20right%20paint%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20ways%20to%20improve%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20general%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20to%20stick%20with%20neutral%20colors%20that%20make%20a%20space%20feel%20bright%20and%20airy%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20guess%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20selecting%20the%20right%20color%20for%20your%20space.%20One%20of%20her%20favorite%20hacks%20is%20to%20spend%20a%20couple%20hundred%20dollars%20on%20a%20consultation%20with%20a%20decorator%20or%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20pay%20somebody%20%24150%20to%20help%20you%20pick%20out%20paint%20colors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bull%2C%20who%20recommends%20going%20to%20your%20local%20paint%20store%20and%20asking%20if%20they%20