%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20leader%20Champai%20Soren%20arrived%20in%20Delhi%20today%20amid%20buzz%20of%20a%20possible%20switch%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20visit%20to%20the%20capital%20has%20sparked%20a%20flurry%20of%20political%20activity%2C%20with%20rumours%20swirling%20about%20his%20potential%20defection%20ahead%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20assembly%20elections%20that%20will%20take%20place%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20arriving%20at%20Delhi's%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20(IGI)%20Airport%2C%20Mr%20Soren%2C%20ignored%20questions%20on%20the%20potential%20defection%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20here%20for%20my%20personal%20work.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20former%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20met%20with%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20in%20Kolkata%20yesterday.%C2%A0Four%20other%20JMM%20leaders%20have%20accompanied%20Mr%20Soren%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20growing%20buzz%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20publicly%20dismissed%20the%20speculations.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20anything%20about%20such%20speculations%20and%20reports...%20I%20am%20where%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren%20took%20office%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jharkhand%20in%20February%20this%20year%20following%20the%20arrest%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20high-profile%20money%20laundering%20case.%20His%20tenure%20as%20the%2012th%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Jharkhand%20was%20brief%2C%20as%20he%20resigned%20in%20July%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20Hemant%20Soren%20to%20resume%20his%20role%20as%20the%20state's%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20Mr%20Soren's%20visit%20to%20Delhi%20has%20fueled%20speculation%2C%20particularly%20as%20he%20is%20set%20to%20meet%20with%20BJP%20leaders%20during%20his%20stay.%20This%20development%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%