3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Prime%20Purveyors%20Of%20Hate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%201%2C%20after%20facing%20Khelif%20for%20a%20whopping%2045-second%20battle%2C%20Italian%20boxer%20Angela%20Carini%20forfeited%20the%20match.%20Later%2C%20she%20would%20tell%20the%20press%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20been%20punched%20so%20hard%26quot%3B%20and%20shed%20tears%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera%2C%20as%20anyone%20would%20have%20in%20her%20position.%20However%2C%20seeing%20a%20white%20woman%20cry%20on%20television%20was%2C%20of%20course%2C%20too%20much%20to%20bear%20for%20champions%20of%20women's%20rights%20like%20author%20J.%20K.%20Rowling%2C%20who%20has%20had%20a%20history%20of%20making%20transphobic%20comments.%20Rowling%20cried%20foul%20on%20X%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Bman%26quot%3B%20punching%20a%20woman%20and%20about%20men's%20rights%20activism%20having%20gone%20too%20far.%20Even%20the%20owner%20of%20X%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20could%20not%20resist%20chiming%20in.%20It's%20another%20story%20that%20Musk's%20own%20views%20about%20transgender%20persons%20are%20worth%20some%20scrutiny%20and%20may%20be%20best%20described%20by%20his%20estranged%20daughter%20who%20he%20refuses%20to%20acknowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Imane%20Khelif%20case%20underlines%20a%20hard%20but%20unsurprising%20truth%3A%20we%20are%20not%20as%20progressive%20in%202024%20as%20we%20would%20like%20to%20believe.%20Sure%2C%20there%20are%20more%20people%20today%20who%20are%20accepting%20of%20queer%20rights%2C%20gender%20equality%2C%20and%20just%20human%20rights%20in%20general%2C%20but%20in%20the%20country%20called%20the%20internet%2C%20this%20population%20is%20sparse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrans%20Hate%20Is%20Misogyny%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20two%20people%20with%20a%20combined%20following%20of%20over%20200%20million%20people%20put%20out%20such%20derogatory%20posts%20against%20a%20woman%2C%20their%20legions%20of%20followers%20are%20bound%20to%20spew%20out%20the%20same%20misinformation%2C%20often%20with%20vile%20language.%20But%20Rowling%20and%20Musk's%20comments%20also%20fanned%20the%20fire%20of%20deep-rooted%20transphobia%20and%20misogyny%20that%20still%20burns%20in%20all%20stratas%20of%20human%20classes%2C%20races%2C%20and%20nationalities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrans%20hate%20is%20just%20another%20catalyst%20for%20overall%20misogyny.%20Groups%20abound%20on%20Reddit%20and%20Facebook%20where%20people%20aligned%20with%20the%20Rowling%20ideology%20simply%20attack%20any%20female%20celebrity%20they%20don't%20think%20is%20%26quot%3Bwoman%20enough%26quot%3B%20and%20must%20therefore%2C%20be%20a%20transsexual%20or%20transgender%3B%20there%20is%20a%20word%20for%20this%20group%20too%2C%20%26quot%3Btransvestigators%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20like%20to%20lift%20weights%20and%20be%20muscular%2C%20then%20you%20are%20not%20feminine%2C%20and%20hence%20make%20for%20a%20perfect%20target%20for%20these%20'tranvestigators'.%20Like%20sports%3F%20Big%20cars%3F%20Not%20dainty%2C%20petite%2C%20blonde%2C%20and%20light-eyed%20enough%3F%20Wear%20too%20much%20makeup%20as%20if%20to%20hide%20male%20appearance%3F%20Wear%20too%20little%20makeup%20because%20you%20are%20a%20man%20trying%20to%20pass%20off%20as%20a%20'sporty%20woman'%3F%20Well%2C%20women%20who%20exhibit%20such%20traits%20%26quot%3Baren't%20women%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20tranvestigators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%20to%20the%20hate%20campaign%20against%20Khelif.%20Soon%20after%20her%20win%20in%20Paris%20and%20its%20fallout%2C%20conservative-leaning%20media%20outlets%20and%20social%20media%20handles%20started%20talking%20about%20her%202023%20disqualification%20by%20the%20International%20Boxing%20Association%20(IBA)%20for%20failing%20a%20'gender%20eligibility%20test'.%20No%20matter%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20IBA%20itself%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20Olympics%20for%20their%20'methods'%20and%20that%20there%20have%20been%20accusations%20of%20corruption%20as%20well.%20The%20International%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOC)%20banned%20the%20IBA%20last%20year%20over%20its%20governance%20and%20finance%20issues%2C%20with%20the%20Olympic%20body%20allowing%20the%20boxing%20competition%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Paris.%20But%20alas%2C%20this%20grain%20of%20truth%20was%20buried%20deep%20under%20the%20rubble%20of%20misinformation%20that%20flooded%20the%20internet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20amid%20this%20storm.%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20'he'%20be%20a%20woman%3F%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BIBA%20must%20have%20banned%20'him'%20for%20a%20reason!%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BXY%20is%20a%20man!%20Only%20men%20have%20Testosterone!%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20clearly%20looks%20like%20a%20man.%20He%20is%20built%20like%20a%20man.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet's%20try%20to%20answer%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMan%2C%20Woman%2C%20Other%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhelif's%20story%20is%20very%20%3Cem%3EDangal%3C%2Fem%3E-like.%20Indian%20audiences%2C%20if%20they%20read%20her%20full%20interview%20with%20UNICEF%2C%20may%20relate%20to%20the%20story%20of%20a%20young%20girl%20joining%20a%20sport%20that's%20dominated%20by%20men.%20But%20unlike%20%3Cem%3EDangal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20did%20not%20have%20a%20father%20ready%20to%20fight%20the%20world.%20She%20fought%20mostly%20alone%20in%20her%20childhood%2C%20while%20her%20family%20battled%20poverty%20to%20feed%20their%20children%20and%20sustain%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20fact%20that%20Algeria%20is%20a%20deeply%20religious%20Islamic%20country%2C%20where%20being%20trans%20may%20invite%20a%20host%20of%20legal%20challenges.%20If%20any%20of%20the%20'tranvestigators'%20like%20Rowling%20or%20Musk%20followers%20had%20bothered%20to%20do%20a%20simple%20Google%20search%2C%20they%20would%20know%20Algeria%20would%20probably%20never%20send%20a%20'trans'%20person%20to%20represent%20their%20country%20in%20the%20Olympics.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EXX%20or%20XY%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoesn't%20matter%2C%20honestly.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20studied%20genetics%20and%20chromosomes%20can%20answer%20this%3A%20the%20set%20of%20chromosomes%20that%20define%20sex%20(not%20gender)%20are%20named%20so%20based%20on%20their%20shape.%20Zoya%20Fatima%2C%20a%20teacher%20at%20Jamia%20Senior%20Secondary%20School%2C%20explains%20that%20women%20have%20two%20chromosomes%20shaped%20like%20'X'%2C%20while%20in%20men%2C%20one%20of%20them%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20'Y'.%20%26quot%3BGenetic%20mutation%20can%20cause%20a%20foetus%20with%20XX%20to%20have%20a%20Y-shaped%20chromosome%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explains%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20can%20have%20all%20female%20genitalia%2C%20even%20uterus%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20but%20ovaries%20in%20almost%20all%20cases%20are%20non-functional.%20But%20they%20can%20be%20mothers%20via%20IVF%20and%20have%20normal%20pregnancies.%20So%20it%20is%20incorrect%20to%20say%20that%20all%20XY%20automatically%20classify%20as%20male%20and%20man.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20were%20to%20go%20by%20the%20definitions%20recommended%20by%20conservative%20social%20media%2C%20then%20millions%20of%20women%20would%20immediately%20lose%20their%20right%20to%20be%20called%20a%20woman%20for%20having%20elevated%20testosterone%20levels.%20While%20testosterone%20is%20considered%20the%20'male%20hormone'%2C%20women%20produce%20it%20too%20-%20many%20with%20hormonal%20disorders%2C%20such%20as%20PCOS%2C%20tend%20to%20produce%20too%20much%20of%20it.%20Will%20these%20conditions%20void%20a%20woman's%20right%20to%20be%20called%20a%20'woman'%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20consider%20science%20for%20our%20definitions%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20women%20with%20XY%20or%20XXY%20or%20XXYY%20chromosomal%20structures%20have%20one%20common%20denominator%3A%20a%20non-functional%20ovary.%20So%20that%20begs%20the%20question%2C%20is%20a%20perfectly%20functional%20ovary%20fundamental%20for%20being%20classified%20as%20a%20'woman'%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20what%20about%20a%20few%20thousand%20women%20who%20have%20ovarian%20insufficiency%3F%20Will%20they%20cease%20to%20be%20known%20as%20women%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Question%20Of%20Race%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20of%20colour%20who%20don't%20fit%20conservative%20definitions%20of%20femininity%20have%20always%20had%20it%20worse.%20Barely%20a%20day%20before%20her%20match%2C%20Khelif's%20Hungarian%20opponent%2C%20Luca%20Hamori%2C%20posted%20an%20incendiary%20picture%20on%20Instagram%20that%20showed%20Khelif%20as%20a%20'beast'.%20For%20centuries%20now%2C%20Black%20women%20have%20been%20mocked%20for%20their%20'masculinity'.%20Not%20too%20far%20in%20India%20itself%2C%20sprinter%20Duttee%20Chand%20had%20been%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20primitive%20gender%20tests.%20%26quot%3BIn%202014%2C%20I%20challenged%20the%20IOC's%20rule%20that%20a%20person%20with%20a%20higher%20testosterone%20level%20should%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20in%20Switzerland.%20It%20was%20noted%20that%20hormonal%20levels%20cannot%20increase%20athletic%20performance.%20I%20suffered%20a%20lot%20at%20that%20time.%20I%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20controversy%20regarding%20my%20gender%2C%26quot%3B%20Chand%20told%20%3Cem%3EPTI%20%3C%2Fem%3Eafter%20the%20Imane%20Khelif%20controversy%20erupted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20abuse%20and%20attacks%20Imane%20Khelif%20has%20faced%20online%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20years%20to%20come.%20The%20key%20takeaway%20is%20this%3A%20misinformation%20driven%20by%20racist%2C%20misogynist%20ideologies%20often%20travels%20much%2C%20much%20faster%20than%20the%20truth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anwiti%20Singh%20is%20Assistant%20Producer%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723959960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F1pqs9278_imane-khelif_625x300_18_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fimane-khelif-and-the-scourge-of-transvestigators-6362533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20kind%20of%20bullying%20and%20abuse%20Olympic%20boxer%20Imane%20Khelif%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20makes%20one%20thing%20clear%3A%20in%20the%20age%20of%20social%20media%2C%20misinformation%20is%20easiest%20to%20amplify%20when%20it's%20rooted%20in%20misogyny%2C%20transphobia%20and%20racism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fimane-khelif-and-the-scourge-of-transvestigators-6362533%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BPCL%20plans%20to%20invest%20Rs%201.7%20trn%20to%20expand%20core%20business%2C%20new%20energy%20foray%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723959454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F18%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1723959367-4334.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbpcl-plans-to-invest-rs-1-7-trn-to-expand-core-business-new-energy-foray-124081800106_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20is%20targeting%20net%20zero%20carbon%20emissions%20from%20its%20operations%20by%202040%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbpcl-plans-to-invest-rs-1-7-trn-to-expand-core-business-new-energy-foray-124081800106_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbpcl-plans-to-invest-rs-1-7-trn-to-expand-core-business-new-energy-foray-124081800106_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbpcl-plans-to-invest-rs-1-7-trn-to-expand-core-business-new-energy-foray-124081800106_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thangalaan'%20box%20office%20collection%20day%203%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723958364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112601937%2Cimgsize-101364.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fthangalaan-box-office-collection-day-3-chiyaan-vikrams-film-surpasses-rs-50-crore-globally%2Farticleshow%2F112601958.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112601958.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThangalaan%2C%20starring%20Chiyaan%20Vikram%2C%20premiered%20on%20August%2015%20and%20saw%20record-breaking%20numbers%20on%20its%20opening%20day.%20Although%20it%20faced%20a%20drop%20on%20its%20second%20day%2C%20the%20film%20rebounded%20on%20Saturday%2C%20earning%20Rs%2014%20crore%20globally%20on%20its%20third%20day.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fbox-office%2Fthangalaan-box-office-collection-day-3-chiyaan-vikrams-film-surpasses-rs-50-crore-globally%2Farticleshow%2F112601958.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Are%20India's%20No%201...%26quot%3B%3A%20IAS%20Coaching%20Centre%20Fined%20For%20%26quot%3BMisleading%26quot%3B%20Ad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20coaching%20institute%20for%20the%20civil%20services%20exam%20has%20been%20fined%20Rs%20three%20lakh%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20advertisements%2C%20the%20Centre%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20said%20that%20the%20Central%20Consumer%20Protection%20Authority%20(CCPA)%20has%20taken%20action%20against%20Sriram's%20IAS%2C%20which%20has%20its%20centers%20in%20Delhi%2C%20for%20a%20misleading%20advertisement%20regarding%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Service%20Exam%20(CSE)%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20the%20Ministry%C2%A0said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCoaching%20institutes%20and%20online%20edtech%20platforms%20use%20pictures%20and%20names%20of%20the%20same%20successful%20candidates%20to%20influence%20prospective%20aspirants%20(consumers)%2C%20without%20disclosing%20the%20courses%20opted%20by%20such%20candidates%20and%20length%20of%20the%20course%20so%20attended%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20and%20promote%20the%20rights%20of%20consumers%20as%20a%20class%20and%20ensure%20that%20no%20false%20or%20misleading%20advertisement%20is%20made%20of%20any%20goods%20or%20services%20which%20contravenes%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%2C%202019%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESriram's%20IAS%20in%20its%20advertisement%20made%20the%20following%20two%20claims%3A%20%26quot%3B200%20plus%20selections%20in%20UPSC%20Civil%20Service%20Exam%202022%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20India's%20No%201%20Prestigious%20UPSC%2FIAS%20Coaching%20Institute%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCPA%20found%20out%20that%20Sriram's%20IAS%20advertised%20various%20types%20of%20courses%20but%20the%20information%20for%20the%20course%20opted%20by%20the%20advertised%20successful%20candidates%20in%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%202022%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeliberately%20concealed%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20advertisement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20the%20effect%20of%20consumers%20falsely%20believing%20that%20all%20the%20successful%20candidates%20claimed%20by%20the%20Institute%20had%20opted%20for%20the%20paid%20courses%20advertised%20by%20the%20Institute%20on%20its%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20regarding%20the%20course%20opted%20by%20successful%20candidates%20is%20important%20for%20the%20consumers%20to%20know%20so%20that%20they%20can%20make%20informed%20choices%20while%20deciding%20which%20course%20and%20coaching%20institute%20to%20join%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESriram's%20IAS%20in%20its%20response%20submitted%20the%20details%20of%20only%20171%20successful%20candidates%20against%20its%20claim%20of%20200%20plus%20selections%20in%20UPSC%20CSE%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOut%20of%20these%20171%20candidates%2C%20102%20were%20from%20the%20Free%20Interview%20Guidance%20Programme%20(IGP)%2C%2055%20were%20from%20the%20Free%20Test%20Series%2C%20nine%20were%20from%20General%20Studies%20classroom%20course%20and%20five%20candidates%20were%20from%20different%20States%20under%20the%20MoU%20signed%20between%20the%20State%20Government%20and%20the%20Institute%20to%20provide%20free%20coaching.%20This%20fact%20was%20not%20disclosed%20in%20their%20advertisement%2C%20thereby%20deceiving%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMajority%20of%20candidates%20had%20already%20cleared%20Preliminary%20and%20Mains%20examinations%20by%20themselves%2C%20with%20no%20contribution%20of%20Sriram's%20IAS.%20By%20concealing%20this%20important%20fact%2C%20such%20false%20and%20misleading%20advertisement%20creates%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20those%20consumers%20who%20are%20UPSC%20aspirants%20without%20letting%20them%20know%20that%20Sriram's%20IAS%20had%20offered%20guidance%20to%20only%20such%20successful%20candidates%20who%20had%20already%20cleared%20Preliminary%20and%20Mains%20examinations%20of%20the%20UPSC%20examination.%20Thus%2C%20the%20advertisement%20has%20violated%20the%20consumer's%20right%20to%20be%20informed%20so%20as%20to%20protect%20himself%20against%20unfair%20trade%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20commissioner%20of%20CCPA%2C%20Nidhi%20Khare%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20an%20advertisement%20should%20contain%20a%20%26quot%3Btruthful%20and%20honest%26quot%3B%20representation%20of%20facts%20by%20disclosing%20important%20information%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bclear%2C%20prominent%20and%20extremely%20hard%26quot%3B%20to%20miss%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723958340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Frmi3h1qg_upsc-exam_625x300_18_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsrirams-ias-coaching-centre-fined-rs-3-lakh-for-misleading-ad-6362347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20famous%20coaching%20institute%20for%20UPSC%20civil%20services%20exam%20preparation%20has%20been%20fined%20Rs%203%20lakh%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20advertisements%2C%20the%20Centre%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsrirams-ias-coaching-centre-fined-rs-3-lakh-for-misleading-ad-6362347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Markets%20to%20take%20cues%20from%20global%20trends%2C%20FII%20trading%20activity%3A%20Analysts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723956470000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F12%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1723434813-3127.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmarkets-to-take-cues-from-global-trends-fii-trading-activity-analysts-124081800079_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Easing%20fears%20of%20a%20recession%20in%20the%20US%20triggered%20a%20global%20market%20rally%20on%20Friday%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fmar