%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%2C%20Ukraine%20Were%20Set%20For%20Ceasefire%20Talks%20In%20Doha.%20Then%20A%20Shock%20Assault%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUkraine%20and%20Russia%20were%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20engaging%20in%20indirect%20ceasefire%20negotiations%20in%20Qatar's%20Doha%20this%20month.%20The%20discussions%2C%20mediated%20by%20Qatar%2C%20aimed%20at%20halting%20the%20destructive%20strikes%20on%20energy%20and%20power%20infrastructure%20that%20have%20plagued%20both%20countries%20since%20the%20conflict%20began.%20However%2C%20a%20diplomatic%20breakthrough%2C%20which%20could%20have%20marked%20de-escalation%20in%20the%20ongoing%20war%2C%20was%20derailed%20by%20Ukraine's%20surprise%20ground%20offensive%20in%20Russia's%20western%20Kursk%20region%2C%20the%20Washington%20Post%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2F08%2F17%2Fkursk-ukraine-russia-energy-ceasefire%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20both%20Kyiv%20and%20Moscow%20had%20signalled%20their%20willingness%20to%20negotiate%20an%20agreement%20that%20would%20stop%20the%20relentless%20attacks%20on%20their%20respective%20energy%20grids%20-%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20caused%20widespread%20suffering%20and%20economic%20turmoil%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ukraine's%20sudden%20incursion%20into%20Kursk%2C%20a%20strategic%20region%20where%20Kyiv%20has%20been%20intensifying%20its%20military%20operations%2C%20threw%20these%20plans%20into%20disarray.%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20confirmed%20on%20Saturday%20that%20his%20forces%20were%20consolidating%20their%20positions%20in%20Kursk%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20focal%20point%20of%20Ukrainian%20military%20efforts%20for%20over%2011%20days.%20This%20offensive%2C%20intended%20to%20disrupt%20Russian%20supply%20routes%20and%20troop%20movements%2C%20coincided%20with%20Moscow's%20accusations%20that%20Ukraine%20had%2