Cp%3EIt's%20been%20a%20rocky%20transition%20in%20the%20US%20from%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20vehicles%20to%20EVs.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-misconceptions-about-the-ev-transition-market-sales-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESales%20have%20slowed%2C%20though%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-misconceptions-about-the-ev-transition-market-sales-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20hasn't%20dissipated%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20potential%20solution%20is%20fast%20gaining%20traction%20in%20China%2C%20where%20EVs%20dominate.%20However%2C%20it%20does%20require%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdf4e554-23bd-4130-a6a7-ef2a8ff7a95c%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20EREVs%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20extended-range%20electric%20vehicle%20(EREV)%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20solely%20propelled%20by%20a%20battery%2C%20but%20the%20battery%20itself%20can%20be%20charged%20by%20a%20generator%20that%20requires%20gasoline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20generator%2C%20the%20range%20of%20EREVs%20can%20double%20that%20of%20their%20pure%20EV%20counterparts%2C%20even%20for%20large%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20Stellantis%20NV%20announced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fram-electric-truck-ramcharger-gas-generator-range-charging-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERamcharger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20EREV%20truck%20that%20promises%20a%20690-mile%20driving%20range%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20twice%20that%20of%20the%20Tesla%20Cybertruck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20that%20gas-reliant%20generator%20proposes%20some%20environmental%20trade-offs%20compared%20to%20a%20pure%20EV.%20EREVs%20still%20emit%20pollutants%2C%20but%20one%202020%20study%20published%20in%20the%20Public%20Library%20of%20Science%20found%20that%20the%20overall%20environmental%20impact%20is%20lower%20than%20hybrid%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20propelled%20by%20an%20internal%20combustion%20engine%20and%20an%20electric%20motor%20%E2%80%94%20and%20gas-powered%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20noted%20that%20EREVs%20consume%20about%2015%25%20less%20mineral%20resources%20than%20hybrid%20electric%20vehicles%20and%20about%2035%25%20less%20fossil%20energy%20than%20gas-powered%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20recent%20Bloomberg%20report%2C%20the%20design%20of%20EREVs%20means%20a%20smaller%20battery%20pack%20than%20traditional%20EVs%2C%20reducing%20the%20overall%20costs%20by%20about%20%244%2C000.%20However%2C%20the%20battery%20pack%20is%20larger%20than%20hybrids%2C%20making%20EREVs%20more%20expensive%20than%20typical%20HEVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4876777-b482-4f38-9187-870f75ed4406%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEREVs%20rise%20in%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEREVs%20have%20yet%20to%20catch%20on%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20they're%20fast%20gaining%20traction%20in%20China%2C%20where%20EV%20makers%20are%20seeing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinese-electric-vehicles-byd-selling-record-cars-tesla-competition-deliveries-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord%20sales%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Detroit%20News%2C%20citing%20the%20China%20Automobile%20Dealers%20Association%2C%20the%20country%20saw%20116%2C00%20wholesale%20shipments%20of%20EREVs%20in%202024%2C%20a%20113%25%20increase%20from%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.bbhub.io%2Fprofessional%2Fsites%2F24%2F2431510_BNEFElectricVehicleOutlook2023_ExecSummary.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20New%20Energy%20Finance%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20EREV%20sales%20more%20than%20doubled%20since%20last%20year%20and%20now%20make%20up%2030%25%20of%20China's%20plug-in%20hybrid%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20automakers%20appear%20to%20be%20taking%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20visit%20to%20China%2C%20Ford%20CEO%20Jim%20Farley%20raved%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20EREVs%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bin-between%26quot%3B%20solution%20for%20customers%20at%20the%20Bernstein%20Annual%20Strategic%20Decisions%20Conference%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20EREVs%2C%20%26quot%3Byou%20get%20an%20EV%20and%20you%20have%20700%20miles%20a%20range.%20You'd%20have%20no%20range%20anxiety%20for%20a%20long%20term%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20any%20chargers%2C%20and%20those%20vehicles%20have%20half%20the%20batteries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20adoption%20of%20EREVs%20in%20the%20US%20could%20still%20face%20barriers%20from%20regulators%2C%20manufacturers%2C%20and%20environmentalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Bloomberg%20report%20noted%2C%20EREVs%20may%20not%20be%20classified%20as%20pure%20EVs%2C%20which%20means%20they%20could%20be%20exempt%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuying-electric-car-could-save-caveats-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20GM%20spokesperson%20also%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20EREVs%20are%20%26quot%3Bcomplicated%20and%20costly%26quot%3B%20to%20build.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20because%20they%20rely%20on%20gas%2C%20EREVs%20could%20be%20placed%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20hybrid%20vehicles%2C%20which%20some%20environmentalists%20now%20argue%20don't%20do%20enough%20to%20push%20the%20world%20toward%20zero-emissions%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ramcharger%20is%20set%20to%20be%20the%20second%20EREV%20sold%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20Chevrolet%20Volt%2C%20introduced%20in%202010%2C%20was%20the%20first%20EREV%20but%20was%20discontinued%20in%202019%20as%20it%20was%20marred%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F50-once-beloved-cars-that-have-been-discontinued-2019-3%23chevrolet-volt-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20sales%3C%2