t%20them%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lifetime%E2%80%99s%20worth%20of%20lessons%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20being%20stuck%20in%20a%20landslide%20for%20four%20days%2C%20driving%20through%20crumbling%20roads%20and%20being%20deserted%20without%20fuel%2C%20teach%20you%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20makes%20you%20more%20intuitive%2C%20says%20Angelica.%20Like%20her%20teen%20counterparts%2C%20she%20recalls%20being%20%E2%80%9Cfussy%E2%80%9D%20about%20her%20food%20preferences%2C%20luxuries%20and%20comforts.%20Bad%20weather%20would%20tick%20her%20off.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20time%20she%20spent%20on%20the%20road%2C%20where%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359311%2Fchavni-maratha-camp-lohagad-visapur-fort-pune-maharashtra-heritage-stay-hotel-sustainable-tents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadapt%20to%20the%20local%20diaspora%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20she%20truly%20discovered%20herself%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20discovered%20my%20father%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98I%20came%20to%20respect%20his%20love%20for%20riding%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20trip%20to%20Nandi%20Hills%20in%20school%20days%2C%20Angelica%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20trip%20where%20I%20observed%20how%20seriously%20my%20dad%20took%20motorbike%20riding%2C%20learnt%20the%20proper%20way%20of%20sitting%20on%20the%20bike%20and%20holding%20when%20hairpin%20bends%20approached.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20short%20trips%20taught%20her%20the%20nuances%20of%20becoming%20a%20good%20pillion.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20helping%20my%20dad%20by%20spotting%20traffic%20coming%20from%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20curve%20and%20watching%20out%20for%20road%20crossings.%20These%20things%20helped%20my%20dad%20focus%20on%20the%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98I%20understood%20his%20way%20of%20thinking%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357087%2Fmotorcycle-biking-trips-from-karnataka-to-kashmir-indian-bikers-tejas-g-r-shares-safety-tips-planning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEvery%20trip%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20ups%20and%20downs.%20Ajay%20and%20Angelica%20were%20no%20strangers%20to%20this.%20But%20ironically%20it%20was%20these%20sticky%20moments%20that%20gave%20Angelica%20an%20insight%20into%20her%20dad%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20approaching%20problems.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20perspective%20is%20pretty%20cool%20as%20is%20his%20logical%20bend%20of%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20commends%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98We%20really%20talked%20our%20heart%20out%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20an%20expanse%20of%20white%20undulating%20terrain.%20The%20motorbike%E2%80%99s%20steady%20rumble%2C%20the%20whistling%20wind%2C%20and%20the%20chirp%20of%20a%20lone%20bird%20are%20the%20only%20things%20that%20interrupt%20the%20silence.%20Angelica%20would%20find%20these%20moments%20perfect%20for%20striking%20up%20a%20conversation%20with%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8UkB2a-N0BU%3Fsi%3DpgYk7ML1njdEw1Ch%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECity%20life%20has%20a%20mundaneness%20to%20it%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20under%20the%20same%20roof%20but%20rarely%20have%20quality%20conversations.%E2%80%9D%20The%20bike%20rides%20flipped%20the%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98My%20dad%20began%20to%20see%20that%20he%20could%20count%20on%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDeal%20breakers%E2%80%9D%20is