%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352330%2Fbubble-wrap-replacement-in-india-coconut-coir-sustainable-packaging-startup-seaweed-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20solution%20that%20could%20mirror%20the%20properties%20of%20plastic%20while%20being%20eco-friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cheaper%20than%20paper%2C%20cloth%2C%20and%20jute%20alternatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20quest%20led%20him%20to%20launch%20%E2%80%98Bio%20Reform%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20startup%20that%20manufactures%20compostable%20bags%20using%20corn%20waste%2C%20sugars%2C%20cellulose%2C%20and%20other%20natural%20components%20into%20sustainable%20biopolymers.%20In%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20it%20has%20replaced%20over%20six%20million%20plastic%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azhar%20is%20manufacturing%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedical%20waste%20bags%2C%20garbage%20bags%2C%20food%20pouches%2C%20and%20book%20wraps.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FBioreform-1-1723181120-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360465%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAzhar%20manufactures%20eco-friendly%20carry%20bags%2C%20biomedic