11715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovide%20jobs%20to%20the%20local%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20noting%20the%20high%20migration%20rate%20from%20Devikhal.%20They%20aimed%20to%20reverse%20this%20trend%20by%20giving%20people%20reasons%20to%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20pulled%20off%20this%20mammoth%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAlways%20wanted%20to%20settle%20in%20the%20hills%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%2C%20who%20had%20been%20together%20since%20Class%2010%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358205%2Ftiny-farm-fort-homestay-rishikesh-raghav-ansh-kumar-delhi-architects-cob-sustainable-home%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealways%20knew%20they%20wanted%20to%20settle%20in%20the%20hills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20they%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20that%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20surprisingly%2C%20their%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20USP%20was%20its%20continental%20food.%20Amit%20and%20Shipra%20taught%20their%20staff%20how%20to%20cook%20pizzas%2C%20pastas%2C%20and%20make%20milkshakes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20allure%20of%20having%20continental%20dishes%20in%20a%20village%20was%20fascinating%20to%20both%20locals%20and%20visitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20soared%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20flood%20of%20customers%20and%20a%20stream%20of%20positive%20reviews%20online.%20The%20scenic%20countryside%20view%20made%20waiting%20in%20line%20a%20pleasant%20experience%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202017%2C%20the%20couple%20relocated%20their%20caf%C3%A9%20to%20Lansdowne.%20The%20reason%3F%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20a%20remote%2C%20less%20commercialised%20location