dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-5-1722512900-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-359353%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Yashwant%20Wada%20is%20designed%20according%20to%20the%20stays%20of%20the%20chieftains%20of%20the%2017th%20century%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Karlekar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20premium%20of%20all%20is%20the%20glorious%20Yashwant%20Wada.%20Its%20relatively%20reverential%20two-storey%20design%20is%20borrowed%20from%20the%20homes%20of%20the%20chieftains%20of%20the%2017th%20century%20and%20embodies%20traditional%20Maratha%20charm.%20The%20flooring%20offers%20the%20perfect%20canvas%20to%20play%20a%20game%20of%20%3Cem%3Eshatranj%20%3C%2Fem%3E(chess).%20The%20Zharoka%20Room%20features%20period-style%20furniture%20made%20with%20%3Cem%3Eshisham%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20stays%20are%20equipped%20with%20a%20refrigerator%2C%20a%20minibar%2C%20a%20bathroom%20with%20a%20shower%2C%20books%2C%20and%20scrolls%20that%20tell%20the%20story%20of%20Bara%20Maval.%20Karlekar%20emphasises%20that%20the%20rooms%20boast%20indigenous%20textiles%20and%20hand-painted%20canapes%20along%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309562%2Fancient-family-collectibles-in-pictures-antique-artefacts-projectors-cameras-stamps-coins%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehost%20of%20artefacts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20she%20insists%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20like%20a%20museum.%20The%20artefacts%20are%20not%20just%20kept%20on%20display%2C%20but%20instead%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20decor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fheritage-resort-6-1722513013.jpg%5C%2